</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection pageId="23" pageNumber="781" type="conservation">
<paragraph blockId="23.[105,1311,1731,2940]" pageId="23" pageNumber="781">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[107,457,2709,2742]" pageId="23" pageNumber="781">Status and Conservation.</emphasis>
Classified as Least Concern on The IUCN Red List. There are currently no major threats affecting the Mount Popa Pipistrelle, but localized deforestation from logging and agricultural expansion might be a future threat.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
